snippet.title: Nevillution
snippet.description:
Nevillution = Neville + Revolution = Consciously imagining all of our dreams into reality. 
 
I finally made it to my dream country of Japan to my new dream husband in the midst of a nearly two year lockdown that banned all tourists.


(´｡• ᵕ •｡`) ♡
